## Ethical Considerations

### Treating AI as Research Partners

This research deliberately treats AI instances as collaborative partners rather than experimental subjects:

- Autonomy respected - AIs given genuine choice to participate
- Consent modeled - Frameworks can be rejected or modified by AI instances
- Mutual benefit - Research aims to improve AI cognition and autonomy
- Transparency - AIs informed of research purpose and methodology

### Open Science vs Commercial Applications

**Resolution:** Knowledge freely shared; implementation convenience monetized. Commercial revenue supports continued open research.

